{"tid":1321160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絕食第12天 陳伯等人苦行上禮賓府要求對話 2400 人參與","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:08:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad0faf7b9a616f10ded3916913c186156fe3458","tid":1321160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E7%AC%AC12%E5%A4%A9-%E9%99%B3%E4%BC%AF%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%8B%A6%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E7%A6%AE%E8%B3%93%E5%BA%9C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%88%87%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25AC%25AC12%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258B%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B3%2593%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=0910c05c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25AC%25AC12%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258B%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B3%2593%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&h=b49386db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E7%AC%AC12%E5%A4%A9-%E9%99%B3%E4%BC%AF%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%8B%A6%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E7%A6%AE%E8%B3%93%E5%BA%9C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%88%87%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1/</a><br />\n<br />\n絕食第12天 陳伯等人苦行上禮賓府要求對話 2400 人參與<br />\n<br />\n2019/7/15 &mdash; 19:19<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/5563a222-f53b-403d-9f1c-71f919bd8ef2-1_FVW6h_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F5563a222-f53b-403d-9f1c-71f919bd8ef2-1_FVW6h_1200x0.png&h=71e8ad01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n73 歲的馬屎埔村民「陳伯」陳基裘、 好鄰舍北區教會傳道人陳凱興等人已絕食 12 天，政府一直未有回應要求對話。絕食者今日（15日）黃昏將行動升級，從金鐘海富中心步行至禮賓府，要求與特首林鄭月娥、警務署署長盧偉聰等直接對話，主辦單位指有 2400人參與。<br />\n<br />\n絕食者與大約 70、80名 市民於今日黃昏 7 時，從金鐘海富中心起步。他們高舉「不要鎮壓市民」的橫額，並沿途高呼「林鄭出嚟！」、「不撤不散」等口號。絕食12天的陳伯需要由其他人攙扶。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上近11時，陳凱興指出考慮到陳伯健康情況，醫生建議陳伯先回到金鐘，因此希望「齊上齊落」，一起回到金鐘，參與者響應。示威者把禮賓府當作連儂牆，貼上種種訴求。<br />\n<br />\n昨日（14日）沙田區遊行演變成警民衝突，警方闖入新城市廣場圍捕示威者，絕食者亦有到場聲援示威者。陳伯一度擋在示威者與防暴警察防線之間，跪求警察撤退，讓示威者離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202019-07-1520at2018.17.48_XuxkF_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202019-07-1520at2018.17.48_XuxkF_1200x0.jpeg&h=28d1d15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/486507955435055/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F486507955435055%2F&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=375b29a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/486507955435055/</a>"},{"pid":"829fc627ffa8517ec69eb9eb97a5791b97f1515b","tid":1321160,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"不撤不散？要人和物資？"}]}